Most people don't go to Wordplay until they've finished the puzzle, or are stuck. As the puzzles get harder over the week, the giveaways tend to be fewer.

You'll find spoilers here in the comments as well, since we also come here after finishing the puzzle to praise, criticize, blame, brag, etc. (or if we're really, really stuck).

